科毕业，要去法国读研，于是他决定再到海外创业，经营进口牛肉、燕窝等农副产品。 在一年的奋斗里，生意逐步有了起色，市场马上就要打开，易师傅原本以为好日子又可以开始时，儿子突然瘫了。在重庆看到这台网约车别急着投诉，他 3 个月已经道歉了 1800 次 _ 腾讯新闻"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/v2-aec082251bcd7caa2c4063c00ff1f116_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "46 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624618813"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28KXvsutjtdTEAMaCTEwMTA4MzQyNyD4ju+oBjAAOM4KQA1yCTYyNDYxODgxM3gAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "14_1696432112.510079", "card_id": "Q_624713634", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 30}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "2023 年诺贝尔化学奖颁给了量子点研究者，什么叫做量子点？这一成就能给我们的生活带来什么？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-3e4bf4c50ebd77490b5c38629a31246a_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "38 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/624713634"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I28KXvsutjtdTEAMaCTEwMTEwNDM5NSCE9PSoBjAAOGpADnIJNjI0NzEzNjM0eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "15_1696432112.511986", "card_id": "Q_623978786", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 34}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "如何评价《少女前线 2：追放》的美术品质？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "被美术建模吸引，感觉在二游里已经算 T0 的水平，有没有大佬专业分析分析"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/50/v2-14525ae5c2969574bafeb7881d568f5d_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "36 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/623978786"}}, "attached_info": "CkAI28KXvsutjtdTEAMaCTEwMDk0MTA1MCCvl86oBjAAOIwBQA9yCTYyMzk3ODc4NngAqg